title: El Piano - Malaga
typeOfFood: Vegan, Western, Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Catering, Spanish
description: Opened in Dec 2011, this is another outlet the El Piano restaurant; other locations are in Granada and York, UK. Provides 100% vegan and gluten-free food, served in biodegradable small pine boats; fleets and armadas are also available. Visit their website to learn about El Piano cookbooks. Sept 2013 reported offers Arizona brand beverages that contain honey - pls check.
